					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I don't see this playing into the demo you've got now, but it's just a thought that occurred to me: Many games create a parallax effect by changing the scroll mid-frame (often multiple times). It's trickier because it requires timed code (or a suitable mapper), but it might be cool to change CHR banks mid-frame to get a similar effect combined with the parallax effect you've already got. You know, in case three layers aren't enough for you.</div>

